00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 1=

3
00:01:17,140 --> 00:01:18,060
Darling,

4
00:01:19,300 --> 00:01:20,420
you look beautiful.

5
00:01:23,340 --> 00:01:25,340
You always know how to make me happy.

6
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:24,620
Lu Shaoyuan!

7
00:02:36,060 --> 00:02:36,980
You...

8
00:02:38,940 --> 00:02:41,260
Darling, I'm Gu Nianchi.

9
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:42,900
I'm your husband.

10
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:44,460
What?

11
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:48,860
Did you forget, Brother?

12
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:52,260
You're the one
who begged me to be your stand in.

13
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,299
Lu Shaoyuan,

14
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:55,900
I'm the one who married her!

15
00:02:56,340 --> 00:02:57,180
Oh?

16
00:02:57,380 --> 00:02:58,300
Really?

17
00:02:59,340 --> 00:03:03,660
But the one who spent
the wedding night with her was me.

18
00:03:08,460 --> 00:03:09,780
What exactly is going on?

19
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:28,260
Get out of my sight!

20
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:35,960
(Three Years Ago)

21
00:03:54,500 --> 00:03:55,460
Father!

22
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:00,380
Father!

23
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:02,980
Qiu, run.

24
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:04,819
What's wrong, Father?

25
00:04:04,820 --> 00:04:06,540
It's Gu Nianchi.

26
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:08,640
(Zhuang Yunqiu)
It's Gu Nianchi...

27
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,400
(Zhuang family's eldest daughter)

28
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:10,099
Father.

29
00:04:10,100 --> 00:04:12,940
You must destroy the opium.

30
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:14,419
Father!

31
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:15,780
Go!

32
00:04:21,580 --> 00:04:22,620
Father!

33
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:24,700
Father!

34
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:27,100
Father!

35
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:08,840
(Gu Nianchi, Commander of Yancheng)

36
00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:11,260
It's you.

37
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:15,540
One slipped through the net.

38
00:05:35,260 --> 00:05:36,740
Thank you for saving me, Miss.

39
00:05:37,580 --> 00:05:38,819
What's your name?

40
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:40,020
My name is Zhuang Yunqiu.

41
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:41,100
And you?

42
00:05:42,860 --> 00:05:44,260
My name is Gu Nianchi.

43
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:53,780
Why?

44
00:05:56,540 --> 00:05:58,140
Why?

45
00:06:02,380 --> 00:06:04,420
Today, we stand together
beneath the snow.

46
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:07,060
One day, we'll grow old together.

47
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:10,800
The Zhuang family of North City.
I'll remember that.

48
00:06:11,020 --> 00:06:11,820
Don't worry.

49
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:13,580
Once my eyes recover,

50
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:16,580
I'll come for you
with a grand wedding procession

51
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:18,620
and marry you properly.

52
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:24,380
Didn't you say you'd marry me?

53
00:06:25,940 --> 00:06:28,500
Too many women like you try to
get close to me for their own gain.

54
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:44,380
What a pity.

55
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:28,600
(Three Years Later)

56
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:57,420
Why tattoo it over the scar?

57
00:07:58,980 --> 00:08:01,100
Because I like today's opera.

58
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:03,580
"The Top Scholar Zhang Xie."

59
00:08:04,140 --> 00:08:05,540
What's it about?

60
00:08:06,300 --> 00:08:07,379
It's about Zhang Xie.

61
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:09,060
After becoming the top scholar,

62
00:08:09,180 --> 00:08:11,460
he abandoned the wife
who stood by him through hardship

63
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:14,340
and even tried to kill her.

64
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,620
But she survived.

65
00:08:18,180 --> 00:08:19,260
Later,

66
00:08:21,820 --> 00:08:23,340
they met again.

67
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:27,920
(Xue Wan, the Xue family's eldest daughter)
What a heartless man.

68
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,880
(Lu Shaoyuan,
Gu Nianchi's younger brother)

69
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:48,979
Commander.

70
00:08:48,980 --> 00:08:50,460
What brings you here?

71
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:51,940
Where's the person I want?

72
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:56,460
Why did the opera stop?

73
00:08:57,180 --> 00:08:58,740
Why is it so noisy outside?

74
00:08:58,940 --> 00:09:00,580
(Gu Nianchi.)

75
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:02,780
(You really came.)

76
00:09:03,100 --> 00:09:05,620
The person's not here, Commander.

77
00:09:06,740 --> 00:09:07,780
No matter.

78
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:11,380
Search the place.

79
00:09:11,620 --> 00:09:12,259
Yes, sir.

80
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,060
- Commander, there's really no one here.
- Over there!

81
00:09:14,140 --> 00:09:14,820
Hurry!

82
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:16,380
Keep up!

83
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:18,099
Search everywhere!

84
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:18,820
Yes, sir!

85
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:28,040
(Cheng Yi, Lu Shaoyuan's sworn younger brother)
Sorry, wrong room.

86
00:09:33,460 --> 00:09:35,060
Those look like Gu Nianchi's men.

87
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:37,300
Have they found us?

88
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:41,380
We're not their target.

89
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:43,339
How do you know?

90
00:09:43,340 --> 00:09:44,379
Commander, we found him!

91
00:09:44,380 --> 00:09:45,340
Listen.

92
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:47,100
They've already found him.

93
00:09:48,620 --> 00:09:49,620
Let's continue.

94
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:53,580
Everything here's clean.

95
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:54,340
Look, Commander.

96
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:59,420
Commander.

97
00:10:04,540 --> 00:10:06,060
(Gu Nianchi.)

98
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:08,299
(My uncle Zhuang Xun,)

99
00:10:08,300 --> 00:10:10,860
(is my grand wedding gift for you.)

100
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:14,880
(And in return, you'll make sure to deal
with that traitor to the Zhuang family)

101
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:18,900
(Zhuang Xun, Zhuang Yunqiu's uncle)
(the hound you've begun to suspect, for me too.)

102
00:10:20,020 --> 00:10:20,980
Zhuang Xun,

103
00:10:22,860 --> 00:10:24,940
it really took some effort to find you.

104
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:28,020
Why have you been hiding from me?

105
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:29,619
Commander...

106
00:10:29,620 --> 00:10:31,580
I haven't.

107
00:10:37,460 --> 00:10:41,020
Where did
the Zhuang family's shipment go?

108
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:44,620
Are you going to tell me yourself,

109
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:46,900
or...

110
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:52,180
Commander,

111
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:55,300
I really don't know.

112
00:10:57,340 --> 00:10:58,500
So,

113
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:01,460
you've chosen the second option.

114
00:11:08,180 --> 00:11:08,939
Commander, please!

115
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:09,819
I really don't know!

116
00:11:09,820 --> 00:11:11,140
Please spare me, Commander!

117
00:11:15,460 --> 00:11:17,700
Commander!

118
00:11:19,700 --> 00:11:20,740
Does it hurt?

119
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:25,179
That scream just now
made my hand slip a little.

120
00:11:25,180 --> 00:11:26,300
Sorry about that.

121
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:30,179
Gu Nianchi really is just as you said.

122
00:11:30,180 --> 00:11:31,980
A cruel and merciless man.

123
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:33,620
That's right.

124
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:35,860
He was born an executioner.

125
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:38,380
To him, this sort of thing

126
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:40,180
is nothing unusual.

127
00:11:41,500 --> 00:11:42,580
(But...)

128
00:11:42,660 --> 00:11:44,540
(only ruthless measures)

129
00:11:44,780 --> 00:11:47,100
(can bring justice to men like Zhuang Xun.)

130
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:57,460
Well?

131
00:11:58,460 --> 00:12:00,140
Do you remember now?

132
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:01,979
Commander...

133
00:12:01,980 --> 00:12:03,619
I remember now.

134
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:06,980
I only found out
about this secret recently.

135
00:12:07,580 --> 00:12:09,100
The shipment you're looking for

136
00:12:09,140 --> 00:12:10,539
was hidden by the Zhuang family

137
00:12:10,540 --> 00:12:13,100
inside a flower.

138
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:21,700
A flower?

139
00:12:24,580 --> 00:12:25,539
What flower?

140
00:12:25,540 --> 00:12:26,139
This...

141
00:12:26,140 --> 00:12:26,979
I...

142
00:12:26,980 --> 00:12:29,100
I really don't know.

143
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:33,700
You're marrying in my place tomorrow.

144
00:12:33,900 --> 00:12:36,420
Why insist on tattooing
a red spider lily here?

145
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:39,979
A red spider lily
blooms for a thousand years,

146
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:41,520
then withers for another thousand years.

147
00:12:41,540 --> 00:12:43,340
Its flowers and leaves
are never seen together.

148
00:12:44,100 --> 00:12:45,620
Love defies fate,

149
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:47,980
yet destiny
still ends in life and death.

150
00:12:49,860 --> 00:12:51,380
Are you regretting this now?

151
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:54,020
The Commander is cruel and merciless,

152
00:12:54,540 --> 00:12:56,699
and I never wanted an arranged marriage.

153
00:12:56,700 --> 00:12:58,220
So I don't want to marry him.

154
00:12:58,740 --> 00:13:00,340
If you're regretting it...

155
00:13:02,460 --> 00:13:03,860
How could I regret it?

156
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:05,580
On the contrary,

157
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:07,580
I'm actually looking forward

158
00:13:07,700 --> 00:13:09,180
to going to the Commander's side.

159
00:13:10,620 --> 00:13:12,020
Then why are you doing this?

160
00:13:15,100 --> 00:13:16,220
As a keepsake.

161
00:13:26,260 --> 00:13:27,900
Who else knows about this?

162
00:13:29,020 --> 00:13:29,980
No one.

163
00:13:30,100 --> 00:13:32,340
I only discovered it recently too.

164
00:13:32,660 --> 00:13:34,460
I never got the chance to tell anyone.

165
00:13:37,060 --> 00:13:38,660
Why should I believe you?

166
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:46,220
Alright.

167
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:48,020
I should go now.

168
00:13:48,380 --> 00:13:50,460
Be careful.

169
00:14:10,620 --> 00:14:11,580
Commander,

170
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:14,260
that's really all I know.

171
00:14:16,100 --> 00:14:18,059
Back then, you and I,

172
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:20,819
and Commander-in-Chief Li too,
worked together from the inside and outside

173
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:22,339
to frame the Zhuang family!

174
00:14:22,340 --> 00:14:25,060
I may not deserve credit,
but I still suffered for it!

175
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:27,539
Commander, please spare me!

176
00:14:27,540 --> 00:14:28,459
I've already told you

177
00:14:28,460 --> 00:14:30,900
everything I know!

178
00:14:32,620 --> 00:14:35,940
You worked with me and Commander-in-Chief Li

179
00:14:36,420 --> 00:14:41,259
to frame the Zhuang family?

180
00:14:41,260 --> 00:14:43,580
Yes...

181
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:50,500
Thank you.

182
00:14:51,780 --> 00:14:54,260
I finally heard what I wanted to hear.

183
00:15:01,020 --> 00:15:01,859
Commander!

184
00:15:01,860 --> 00:15:03,100
Please spare me, Commander!

185
00:15:10,580 --> 00:15:11,820
(Yunqiu,)

186
00:15:12,620 --> 00:15:14,739
(everything happened
just as I expected.)

187
00:15:14,740 --> 00:15:16,779
(The destruction of the Zhuang family)

188
00:15:16,780 --> 00:15:19,220
(was a scheme by Gu Nianchi
and Commander-in-Chief Li.)

189
00:15:19,700 --> 00:15:23,379
(I'll seek justice for you
and your family.)

190
00:15:23,380 --> 00:15:24,380
(Uncle,)

191
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:28,220
(this is the price
for all the wrong you've done.)

192
00:15:29,100 --> 00:15:30,420
(Once you're gone,)

193
00:15:31,900 --> 00:15:33,700
(make peace with the Zhuang family.)

194
00:15:36,060 --> 00:15:38,180
(As for the one who'll kill you...)

195
00:16:46,380 --> 00:16:49,460
(White spider lilies bloom in heaven,)

196
00:16:50,180 --> 00:16:53,020
(while red spider lilies bloom in hell.)

197
00:16:54,180 --> 00:16:55,620
(Gu Nianchi,)

198
00:16:57,520 --> 00:16:59,400
(tomorrow, I'll marry you.)

199
00:17:01,070 --> 00:17:03,490
(I'll be waiting for you in hell)

200
00:17:04,220 --> 00:17:06,760
(with these red spider lilies.)

201
00:17:15,120 --> 00:17:19,810
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

202
00:17:21,120 --> 00:17:26,440
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

203
00:17:26,940 --> 00:17:30,520
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

204
00:17:30,860 --> 00:17:33,870
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

205
00:17:34,040 --> 00:17:39,160
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

206
00:17:40,280 --> 00:17:45,470
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

207
00:17:46,530 --> 00:17:52,130
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

208
00:17:52,670 --> 00:17:56,050
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

209
00:17:56,300 --> 00:17:59,249
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

210
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:04,389
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

211
00:18:04,390 --> 00:18:08,709
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

212
00:18:08,710 --> 00:18:11,289
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

213
00:18:11,290 --> 00:18:13,569
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

214
00:18:13,570 --> 00:18:17,119
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

215
00:18:17,120 --> 00:18:21,649
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

216
00:18:21,650 --> 00:18:24,180
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

217
00:18:24,320 --> 00:18:26,269
♪Still I walk into♪

218
00:18:26,270 --> 00:18:29,869
♪The trap you set without regret♪

219
00:18:29,870 --> 00:18:33,919
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

220
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:36,499
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

221
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:38,659
♪A stand in can never cross♪

222
00:18:38,660 --> 00:18:42,099
♪The shortest distance between us♪

223
00:18:42,100 --> 00:18:47,070
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

224
00:18:47,230 --> 00:18:51,900
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

225
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:56,249
♪A substitute♪

226
00:18:56,250 --> 00:19:01,250
♪Needs no reason♪

